Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultranate?! But that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All orbital attack satellites have been destroyed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. We can proceed to stage three of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding to stage three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu energy, switch to line A!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open transmission antennas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transmission antennas, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adjusting angles. Unit 1, plus 0.8 Unit 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Final adjustment, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Mr. Hargen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence transmission of Raggu energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:05.09,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're completely part of me, I don't want to hold back anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:09.32,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember, we got GD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.87,English,,0000,0000,0000,,If curiosity moves in the point of the compass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.87,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Then most likely the special power will arise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:20.00,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent city, we're salvager
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:26.85,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I will one day find the skyscraper of the submerged city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:30.84,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, come together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:41.46,English,,0000,0000,0000,,By passing through time, let's revive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:53.37,English,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things that the sun shines upon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.04,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:04.18,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to convey it to you, I don't want you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.89,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I take you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:14.93,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there is a world awaiting that no one has ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.49,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.23,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:39.86,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,750)\pos(320,322)}A Flower Blooming in Space
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, will you please hand over the data disc?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to do anything about that battleship of his?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The military has thrown together a space battle fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's preparing to scramble to destroy the battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're going to leave Aika and Rion to die, just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall guaranteeing your lives on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give us a chance! You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of that ship even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please! Give us one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu is normally located at various points deep within the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moves freely, carried in the mantle's convection currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great disaster that occurred years ago happened when,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by accident, a great deal of Raggu surfaced simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is to beam Raggu energy down from orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cause the Raggu in the Earth to all simultaneously surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, my aim is to artificially create an earthquake,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hundreds of times more powerful than the one that struck twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The civilization of those foolish apes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall return to nothingness in a very short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the apes themselves, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf... If you do that, you won't survive either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The environment wouldn't support human life after that, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to fear. The environment will be regenerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the whole aim of this project, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To regenerate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's why this ship also carries the DNA sets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of several thousand species of animals and plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The earth and seas shall be reconstructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new ecosystem will form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we shall descend to the new Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall build an ideal human civilization. A Utopia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Utopia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you've guessed by now, the ones who will build this new Utopia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shall be me and the women with me aboard this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be interested in passing my genes to a new generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with you?! No matter how you say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all you're after is to create a harem you can have all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... You can't make me do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gold-buttoned girly man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You curly-haired pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where'd you get that stupid uniform?! Group Sounds? Julie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to pay you back for last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta do something. I've gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta warn Papa and Aika somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't talk, just walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now stay here and keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion! Rion, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you wearing... Oh, no. Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, are you all right? Rion! Rion, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear Aika's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! Aika, is that really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Rion, I'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy. I can't believe you really came back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my precious partner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. If I hadn't messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't say that! Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so happy that you came back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Just a little scraped, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've found you in one piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's get out of here, as fast as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's what Hargen is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, unless we do something, Earth's in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to concentrate on escaping from this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Follow me, and stay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the escape pod?! Show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Neina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she?! A cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you've really got some guts, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What are you doing to Aika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to ask for help? What's wrong, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, if I could have, I never would've let you see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for hiding this until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! That is just so totally cool! Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too cool! So, how do you transform?! You lucky stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful! Like something out of an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ever tell me about something this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can be so mean! Even you, Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit ignoring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small craft rapidly approaching, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but I think it's a national space force vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've no time to waste. Draw it in, then destroy it with one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange. They must have noticed us, but they're doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look sharp, Bandra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft has collided with antenna #3, checking damage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Antenna heavily damaged! Nonfunctional!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transmission output down by 25%!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compensate the output loss with the remaining three antennas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, sir! That'll put much too high a load on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! It'll still be within their specifications!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll transfer inside there, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandra, take us over to the nearest hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vessel has docked with us! Hatch #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get an armed squad down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out! I said cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the way, dammit! Quit daydreaming, will ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, forcing me to come with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gusto, you better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gusto, you handle setting the explosive charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for Rion and Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you show me the way, Miss Meipia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. I'll show you. Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's use this chance to get to the escape pods!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reprogramming, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Antenna load is still within the maximum spec. It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At most, 13% behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hargen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting has just broken out in Area 58, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The report is that there's been considerable damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Route the video over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the surveillance from the lab section room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lab section room, on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry on with the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you guys head for Area 69.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Huh? What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Have you found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I've found them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? My Ultranate is supposed to be greatly superior to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is yours better than mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept it! I absolutely will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her human body can't take the effects of Ultranate any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the fusion of Ultranate and a human is extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how strong a mind or body they may have,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sudden fusion always destroys the human host eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we do anything for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion... Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can already repel the force of this gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The adaptability of Ultranate metal is greater than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultranate metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Great Disaster, researchers were working on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a fluid metal life form to enhance physical strength intensively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it could take the form of a piece of clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When activated, it would then spread over the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a thickness of only a few microns,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,providing armor protection and speed and strength magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been a new era in the art of weapons design.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But its development was very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most test subjects lost their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the project was thought to be a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were reports of a single success with a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it was thought that she and the data on her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were lost after the disaster occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That young girl, Miss Aika... It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I won't be able to use Neina anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now, Miss Aika, I'll make you work for me in her place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that much strength left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Aika's sake, you must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still so immature at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu resonance, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hargen, we've confirmed Raggu resonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll be back in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aika, this time I'll make you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had explosions on the antenna joint
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and throughout the ship! It must be sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll be mine and mine alone, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Neina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'll never let you go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Neina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! If I do, you'll just run off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always there by your side, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, big brother, now you can always care for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it's because I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it! Please, Neina, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Raggu energy is reversing! The main cable has burned through!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close all connections to the Raggu reactor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch back to standard power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locking out all reactor connection circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! I can't lock them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The energy in the reactor is backflowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother? What's wrong? Do you hate me now, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to love your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion! Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost the transmitters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't do it! Big brother is mine alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... I won't give him to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back on active duty, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am! Somebody forced me into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother... Big brother... Big brother... Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hargen! Mr. Hargen, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! There's no response from Mr. Hargen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, the Raggu reactor is out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll destroy the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raggu resonance has been completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation has failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.63,0:23:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Get to the escape capsules!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:10.01,Announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going! You can still run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All gunnery personnel have evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?! Come on, this is a short cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running as fast as I can, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Rion eat to make her so heavy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get enough exercise, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say something, Aika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.61,0:24:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys all right? We were getting tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my sweet honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.68,0:24:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gusto! You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.56,0:25:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.26,0:26:09.36,English,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the shining city
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.94,0:26:19.57,English,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds were erased by the sounds of the bells and honks
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.98,0:26:24.78,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that day's heartbeat
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.52,0:26:35.32,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fingertips that I felt were very sad
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.63,0:26:50.98,English,,0000,0000,0000,,If I count the stars and sigh, you overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:59.48,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since more strong feelings are forming little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.48,0:27:06.69,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow it's going to be a new me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.69,0:27:15.37,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I might take a detour by getting lost and by dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.37,0:27:25.07,English,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to meet your smile at my destination
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:46.47,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since more strong feelings are forming little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.47,0:27:53.67,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow it's going to be a new me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.67,0:28:02.35,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I might take a detour by getting lost and by dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.35,0:28:12.02,English,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to meet your smile at my destination
